            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "My two kids are studying in this school, School Management always try to force their orders to us without prior information. I am too much frustrated with the behaviour of this school.\n\nI dont care about the paid reviews done eariler for this school by other people. But this is my honest review.\n\nOne of my kid is studying in MO3, when i went to PTM, every thing was fine, teacher / student feedback was very good, then all of a sudden my kid was transferred to another setion with new class teacher.\n\nI submitted an application to revert her section with previous class teacher and mentioned that my kid is not comfortable with the new class teacher's behavior.\n\nStill there is no positive response from the school.\n\nWhen i raise issues with the online classes, for little kids, they say that this order is from DM. Oh please Mr. DM, are you aware that kids below 6 years are not smart enough to take the online classes, they need a proper guidance to write and learn  and for this we as a parent send them to school. and school send them back to us for online classes, what the f..\n\nI am waiting to complete this session, then i will take my kids out of this school for sure.\n\n#NO_RECOMMENDATION_AT_ALL\n#NOT_THE_BEST_SCHOOL\n\nThis school may be fine for classes above 5th but not for kids before Class 1st.",
